Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Overhrow your oppressors!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These aren't my words{\i}
